  "Description": {
    "English": "An advanced survival technology module that allows expansion of a user's <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Storage</span>.<br><br>Pre-packed nano-expanders create stablised sub-warp voids within the Exosuit, increasing its <span class=\"name name-stellar\">inventory capacity</span>. Apply this augmentation at the Exosuit upgrade terminal on board a <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Space Station</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "用以扩展使用者<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装存储空间</span>的高级生存技术模块。<br><br>预装的纳米扩张器能在套装内生成稳定的次曲速虚空，从而增加<span class=\"name name-stellar\">库存容量</span>。你可以在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">空间站</span>内的套装升级终端处安装这个增强部件。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "能擴充使用者<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝儲存空間</span>的先進生存科技模組。<br><br>內含奈米擴充填料，能在強化套裝中創造穩定的子空間跳躍虛空，進而增加<span class=\"name name-stellar\">道具欄容量</span>。可在<span class=\"name name-stellar\">太空站</span>上的強化套裝升級終端站套用此擴充。"
  },
